# Licensing Ocean Agents

Except for the exclusions and third-party materials described below, Ocean
Agents source code is available under either of these licenses, at your option:

- the Apache License, Version 2.0 ([`LICENSE-APACHE`](LICENSE-APACHE)); or
- the MIT License ([`LICENSE-MIT`](LICENSE-MIT)).

Copyright © 2026 Rising Tides.

## Documentation and project-authored assets

Project-authored documentation, reusable profiles, package manifests, and
non-brand assets in this repository are available under the same
`MIT OR Apache-2.0` choice unless a file or directory states different terms.

## Brand exclusion

Ocean names, logos, wordmarks, and other distinctive brand assets are not
licensed under the open-source licenses above. Reasonable nominative use remains
allowed as described in [`TRADEMARKS.md`](TRADEMARKS.md). Source code surrounding
or generating a brand asset remains under the project license; the resulting
brand identity does not.

## Third-party material

Third-party code, fonts, and icons remain under their respective licenses. See
[`NOTICE.md`](NOTICE.md), [`docs/PROVENANCE.md`](docs/PROVENANCE.md),
[`docs/provenance.json`](docs/provenance.json), local license files, source
headers, and dependency manifests. Those terms continue to apply regardless of
which Ocean license you select.

Unless required by an upstream license or agreed in writing, contributions
submitted to this repository are licensed under this same project licensing
posture.
